T*(Library of Congress                             Árpád Goretity)Tj
T*(Copyright Office                                7 Kaptárkő st.)Tj
T*(101 Independence Avenue, S.E.                   Budapest, Hungary)Tj
T*(Washington, D.C. 20559-6000                     01/25/2012)Tj
T*()Tj
T*()Tj
T*(Dear Office,)Tj
T*()Tj
T*()Tj
T*(Last summer I was really glad to encounter the approval of the DMCA exception)Tj
T*(that legally allows the jailbreaking and unlocking of smartphones. Freedom of)Tj
T*(software and hardware plays an important role in nowadays' modern computing.)Tj
T*()Tj
T*(As the expiration date of this exception is getting sooner, I'd like to express)Tj
T*(my concord with it. Smartphone users, hobbyists, developers \(including myself\),)Tj
T*(researchers and other computer experts need the ability to really own their)Tj
T*(devices in order to get the best results regarding usability, ergonomy and general)Tj
T*(interoperability. I'm looking forward to the renewal of this exception which makes)Tj
T*(present-day smartphone systems really smart.)Tj
T*()Tj
T*()Tj
T*(Yours faithfully,)Tj
T*()Tj
T*(                Árpád Goretity)Tj
T*()Tj
ET
endstream
